title: Ageha Relax Cafe
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Japanese, Organic, Beer/Wine, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Menu items containing dairy and eggs are marked as such, in Japanese (no English menu). Around 4 set dinner meals can be made vegan. Some desserts are vegan. Couch with armchair, table and chair seating in a warm atmosphere.
